SECTION IX
A PPLICATION OF THE S YSTEM

The dynamic Administration and Academic performance Management System is the software application that we have carried out through this research paper. Dynamic Administration Management System provides all the features to execute wide range of Academic, Administrative, Security, Services and maintain all from a single database. The interface is simple to use and user friendly. The system is based on Content Management System(CMS) technology for the realization of presentation. The implementation is flexible and scalable, by means of using open source CMS and popular technologies for enterprise application development and integration. The important feature of the system is spreading the work of applications for distributed automation over the intranet network of the University. The figure below shows the main interface of the system.
Figure 5
Fig. 5. Main Interface of the system.

