SECTION XI
M ESSAGING M ANAGEMENT T OOL

Every user can send and receive message inside the system, but there are some restrictions which user can not send message to everyone as he wish to, and every user can send and receive email to the user of the same group or to the parent. According to hierarchy the users of specific department can send and receive only within his/her department. The restriction is flexible and can be removed according to the administration. The figure below shows how messaging tool works.
Figure 7
Fig. 7. Messaging tool.

